    * A boldDebt increase  of ( stake * [L_boldDebt - L_boldDebt(0)] )
    *
    * Where L_ETH(0) and L_boldDebt(0) are snapshots of L_ETH and L_boldDebt for the active Trove taken at the instant the stake was made
